---
title: Poached Chicken Salad with Toasted Sesame Dressing and Crispy Wonton
description: Poaching in this dish helps to keep the chicken moist while infusing it with Chinese five spice. Topping it off with a tangy and sweet peanut butter chili sauce. And forget the crustons because we've got crispy fried wontons!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poached-chicken-salad-bd90924a.jpg
